Make a self-contained minimal package.

FILES
======
rdf.c           main source code
zcom.h          common modules (abridged)
Makefile        build file (for distribution)
rdf.cfg         typical configuration file
README          this file

Usage
=====
To compile: enter 
    make 
under Linux, or under windows (assuming visual C++)
    cl rdf.c

To run: edit `rdf.cfg' for parameters, then type 
  ./rdf 
for Linux or 
  rdf
under windows

